original: Montalvo, Tage Ulrik Sixten, direktör, Varberg, f. 11/5/03 i Växjö. G. 31 m. Sigrid Halden. Barn: Sonja f. 34, Mona 36, Tor 41. — Stud. v. Växjö h. a. 1. samt v. hand:sk., språkstud. Kont :prakt. i Sthlm 19-22, anst. v. TT 22-24, Heijnes Byrå 24-26, Pressens Report :byrå i Sthlm 26-33, övert. Var-bergs Trikåfabr. 33. Led. av stads-fullm. o. dess beredn :utsk. 40, löne- o. avtindn 42, hamnstyr. 40, styr. f. Var-bergs samrealsk. 37, rev. i arbilösh:-ndn 38, ordf. i Tidn. Vestkustens Tryckeri A-B 37-38, HaiH. ungsv. distr. 40-42 samt li Varbergs höger för en. 43-45, led. av tax:nd 44, ordf. i styr. f. Englo A-B, v. ordf. i Småi. gilile i Varberg sed. 43. Medl. av Frimurarorden o. Par Brico’le.
translated: Montalvo, Tage Ulrik Sixten, director, Varberg, b. 11/5/03 in Växjö. Married 31 with Sigrid Halden. Children: Sonja b. 34, Mona 36, Tor 41. - Studied at Växjö high school until 1, and studied business writing and languages. Worked as a practical intern in Stockholm from 19-22, employed by TT from 22-24, Heijnes Agency from 24-26, Pressens Report Agency in Stockholm from 26-33, took over Varbergs Trikåfabr. in 33. Member of city council and its committee from 40, salary and wage committee from 42, harbour board from 40, board of Varbergs secondary school from 37, auditor in unemployment insurance from 38, chairman of Tidn. Vestkustens Tryckeri A-B from 37-38, HaiH. youth district from 40-42, and Varbergs conservatives from 43-45, member of tax committee from 44, chairman of the board for Englo A-B, vice-chairman of Småi. guild in Varberg since 43. Member of Freemasons and Par Brico'le.
